section.def:
company
                (公司) means the Hongkong and Kowloon Wharf and
            Godown Company Limited, its successors and assigns;

paragraph.content:
the removal from a car park of a vehicle, without notice to the owner thereof,
                in respect of which there has been a contravention of any by-law made pursuant to
                this section, and the fees payable in respect of such removal;
